description: Not your ordinary soft serve ice cream.Tubby's is a mobile ice cream shop. We serve ice cream with fresh toppings made to order. Infused with -320 degree liquid nitrogen, our products are sure to attract everyone's attention. Starting with a high end gourmet ice cream blend we then mix your favorite toppings into the cream to make your very own custom hand crafted dessert following up with a blast of nitrogen to instantly freeze your guilty pleasure.  This mobile trailer can provide hours of entertainment at private parties, special events, corporate events, weddings, festivals and nighttime festivities.Come see us for a sweet and entertaining treat!
name: Tubby's Ice Cream
